title: Two Japanese land on Diaoyu Islands: report
description: Japan’s Maritime Safety Agency said two Japanese citizens landed on Diaoyu Islands at around 9:30 am (Local time), Jiji press reported Tuesday.
cleanContent: Japan’s Maritime Safety Agency said two Japanese citizens landed on Diaoyu Islands at around 9:30 am (Local time), Jiji press reported Tuesday.Identity of the two people can not be immediately confirmed.																																																																								|  |
